personate or defraud individuals."]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white font-bold","children":"Violation of these terms may result in immediate account termination and legal action."}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-black","children":"2. ACCOUNT MANAGEMENT & CREDITS SYSTEM"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"To use FaceSeek's facial search engine, you must create an account and maintain accurate registration information. You are solely responsible for:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-zinc-500","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Account Security:"}]," Maintaining confidentiality of your login credentials and preventing unauthorized access."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Credit Purchases:"}]," Credits purchased for facial recognition searches are non-refundable and represent a license to use our AI processing engine, not a physical product."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Account Activity:"}]," All facial search activities conducted through your account, whether authorized or unauthorized."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Inactive Accounts:"}]," Accounts with no activity for 12 consecutive months may be purged, including unused credits."]}]]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-black","children":"3. FACIAL RECOGNITION ACCURACY & LIMITATIONS"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"FaceSeek uses advanced AI facial recognition algorithms to provide image intelligence services. However, you acknowledge and agree that:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-zinc-500","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"AI Assistance Tool:"}]," Our facial search engine is an investigative assist tool, not a definitive legal proof or identification system."]}],"$L4","$L5","$L6"]}]]}],"$L7","$L8","$L9"]}]}]}],["$La"],"$Lb"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
